frames.caption: A mysterious mermaid with long, dark hair sits on a rocky shore, gazing intently at the viewer. The turbulent sea behind her crashes against the rocks, creating a dramatic and mystical atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a mermaid perched on a rocky coastline during a stormy evening. The setting is mystical and otherworldly, with the ocean waves adding to the dramatic mood.

frames.caption: A woman with wet hair sits by the ocean, wearing a seashell-adorned top. The waves crash behind her against a rocky shoreline under a moody, overcast sky.
frames.description: The scene depicts a woman at the edge of the ocean, possibly on a rocky beach. The atmosphere is dramatic, with turbulent waves and a dark, cloudy sky suggesting an impending storm.

frames.caption: A mysterious figure with glowing eyes emerges from the shadows, her wet hair clinging to her shoulders. The dimly lit scene is set against a rocky backdrop, suggesting a coastal or cave environment.
frames.description: The scene depicts a woman with glowing eyes, standing in a dark, possibly coastal setting. Her wet hair and the glistening water on her skin indicate she has recently emerged from the water. The atmosphere is eerie and enigmatic, with a sense of otherworldliness.
